Class FeedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301.t05.habilect.FeedEvent

  • public class FeedEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates events comprised of a user account and habit event, these events are meant to be put into the social feed so that users can see habit events from their friends
